Package edu.cuny.util.io

I/O-related utility classes.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
DataWriter Interface for logging data to a back-end store.
 

Class Summary
CSVReader A class for reading data from a CSV (comma-separated variables) text file.
CSVWriter A class for writing data to a CSV (comma-separated variables) text file.
DataSeriesWriter A data writer that stores data in a memory-resident data structure that can also be used as a data series model for a JSci graph, or a table model for a swing JTable component.
